# Image assets required for this template
#
# Drop the following images into this directory before publishing:
#
#   hero-apothecary.jpg     — Hero background. Editorial photography of an apothecary
#                              interior or hands working with botanical jars. 2400×1600,
#                              warm tone, low contrast (frame panel sits over left half).
#
#   condition-pain.jpg      — TabsShowcase image. Hands, soft daylight. 1600×1200.
#   condition-sleep.jpg     — Indoor twilight, calm bedroom or window. 1600×1200.
#   condition-anxiety.jpg   — Single figure, soft profile, daylight. 1600×1200.
#   condition-neuro.jpg     — Clinical-warm scene (consultation, brain scan diagram). 1600×1200.
#
#   about-clinic.jpg        — About section. Dr Marques or the practice interior, warm
#                              natural light, editorial register. 2000×1500.
#
#   logo-apothicare.svg     — Brand logo, monochrome, works on both parchment and botanical
#                              dark grounds. Wordmark + small leaf glyph preferred.
#
# Photography direction:
#   - Warm white balance (3200K–4000K)
#   - Natural / window light, no harsh studio strobes
#   - Real clinicians and real apothecary interiors only — no stock-photo doctors
#   - Avoid the green-neon "weed" aesthetic entirely
